creator: Vocom
descriptionHtml: The application includes a detailed guide including the 210 most common types of mushrooms, with detailed descriptions and quality photos. There is also a key for identifying species according to visible signs. The biggest application specialty is the experimental function for optical recognition of mushrooms using neural network. Give it a shot!
descriptionShort: Mushroom recognition application with complex guide and key.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New module with extended gallery of photos of mushrooms in high resolution
- Graphic redesign
- New recognition model
- Added possibility to recognize from saved photos
- French language
- Various bugfixes and tweaks
